  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Provide dignity kits to women in the worst affected districts\r\n\r\nEstablish multipurpose  women centres for vulnerable women in 5 district headquarters to provide dignity kits, solar lamps, trauma counselling, life-saving information, referrals,and to carry out women's safety audits in each district, and to facilitate early recovery and livelihood activities\r\n\r\nEstablish information desks in 3 districts to provide up to date information on humanitarian and recovery services available.\r\n\r\nSupport women's groups with economic empowerment initiatives, including cash for work projects in debris removal"
    },
